        "timestamp": "2018-10-25 18:01:58.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: -Code-Review\n\nCloud owner can be specified directly by requestDetails.cloudConfiguration.cloudOwner if desired. I could not find much information about this issue at the original commit https://jira.onap.org/browse/SO-636 hash \ncd817ddd55b. Marcus can you send me an email to talk about what this was originally trying to solve?",
