        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2018-10-25 18:08:46.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Cloud owner can be specified directly by requestDetails.cloudConfiguration.cloudOwner\n > if desired. I could not find much information about this issue at\n > the original commit https://jira.onap.org/browse/SO-636 hash\n > cd817ddd55b. Marcus can you send me an email to talk about what\n > this was originally trying to solve?\n\nHi Max,\n\nSee this email chain https://lists.onap.org/g/onap-discuss/message/13243 \n\nThere was a proposal in Beijing to send vimId to SO during instantiate requests, the change this if fixing was a bit early for capabilities in VID.",
        "patchset_number": 1
